WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 23=

00:00:05.540 --> 00:00:06.620
Madam,

00:00:08.220 --> 00:00:11.299
I never expected
that while I was bedridden,

00:00:11.300 --> 00:00:12.740
you'd seem so happy about it.

00:00:13.660 --> 00:00:14.620
Dear,

00:00:14.820 --> 00:00:16.499
please let me explain.

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:17.979
Save your excuses.

00:00:17.980 --> 00:00:19.899
We heard everything clearly
outside the door.

00:00:19.900 --> 00:00:21.419
You're a terrible man.

00:00:21.420 --> 00:00:22.620
A heartless man.

00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:25.220
Today, neither of you

00:00:25.260 --> 00:00:26.740
is getting away.

00:00:27.180 --> 00:00:28.299
Close the door.

00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:30.020
Beat them.

00:00:46.580 --> 00:00:47.980
Ow, that hurts!

00:00:53.140 --> 00:00:54.940
Ouch, that hurts!

00:00:55.300 --> 00:00:57.099
Pretty Auntie, don't be sad.

00:00:57.100 --> 00:00:59.579
You'll definitely
have a child of your own someday.

00:00:59.580 --> 00:01:01.699
And with someone who truly loves you,

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:04.220
you'll have a very adorable baby.

00:01:04.580 --> 00:01:06.420
Thank you for comforting me, Suisui.

00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:10.899
I'm not comforting you.

00:01:10.900 --> 00:01:12.140
It's true.

00:01:13.100 --> 00:01:13.820
Madam,

00:01:14.100 --> 00:01:15.940
my daughter never breaks her word.

00:01:19.420 --> 00:01:20.299
What happened today

00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:22.300
was all thanks to the Little Princess.

00:01:23.020 --> 00:01:24.979
From now on,
all the Ning family's rice shops

00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:26.520
will follow the Little Princess's orders.

00:01:26.520 --> 00:01:28.379
Whatever grain she wants,
she shall have it.

00:01:28.380 --> 00:01:29.500
Really?

00:01:30.300 --> 00:01:31.820
Absolutely true.

00:01:32.500 --> 00:01:33.379
Men!

00:01:33.380 --> 00:01:34.299
Open the granaries!

00:01:34.300 --> 00:01:35.500
Distribute the grain!

00:01:36.500 --> 00:01:38.460
That's wonderful, Father!

00:01:42.340 --> 00:01:43.779
Hahaha!

00:01:43.780 --> 00:01:45.220
Good!

00:01:45.260 --> 00:01:48.099
Suisui truly is a lucky star.

00:01:48.100 --> 00:01:49.600
You've only been in the palace
for a few days,

00:01:49.600 --> 00:01:51.620
and you've already
done me such a great service.

00:01:51.820 --> 00:01:52.940
Oh,

00:01:53.020 --> 00:01:56.339
Grandfather, you're
making me embarrassed.

00:01:56.340 --> 00:01:58.700
Hahaha!

00:01:58.780 --> 00:01:59.779
However,

00:01:59.780 --> 00:02:01.340
I never expected

00:02:01.580 --> 00:02:04.500
Wu Wang would also be involved in this.

00:02:04.620 --> 00:02:05.500
Father,

00:02:05.700 --> 00:02:07.099
Wu Wang is the Imperial Preceptor,

00:02:07.100 --> 00:02:09.219
yet he colluded with court officials,

00:02:09.220 --> 00:02:11.900
used schemes to disrupt state affairs
and dark arts to harm people.

00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:13.860
This matter must not be treated lightly.

00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:16.100
I will not let him off lightly.

00:02:16.900 --> 00:02:19.820
I've long thought
that Daoist was suspicious.

00:02:20.020 --> 00:02:21.460
If not for what happened back then...

00:02:22.940 --> 00:02:24.060
Forget it.

00:02:24.340 --> 00:02:26.099
If we catch him this time,

00:02:26.100 --> 00:02:28.740
I'll make sure he faces the consequences
of disrupting the court.

00:02:30.900 --> 00:02:33.820
(What is that smell?
It smells fragrant and foul. It's awful.)

00:02:34.420 --> 00:02:36.299
Uh...

00:02:36.300 --> 00:02:39.820
Grandfather, what is that smell on you?

00:02:39.980 --> 00:02:41.100
Hm?

00:02:44.140 --> 00:02:44.899
Oh.

00:02:44.900 --> 00:02:47.220
This?

00:02:47.620 --> 00:02:48.899
This sachet

00:02:48.900 --> 00:02:50.379
was given to me by Consort Shu.

00:02:50.380 --> 00:02:52.539
She said it was newly made.

00:02:52.540 --> 00:02:54.379
I thought it smelled nice,
so I asked for it.

00:02:54.380 --> 00:02:54.699
What?

00:02:54.700 --> 00:02:55.620
Do you like it?

00:02:59.740 --> 00:03:01.419
Young Mistress, have you forgotten?

00:03:01.420 --> 00:03:03.020
That is exactly the smell on Wu Wang.

00:03:04.140 --> 00:03:05.820
(Could it be...)

00:03:07.980 --> 00:03:09.219
Grandfather,

00:03:09.220 --> 00:03:12.260
do you like the color green?

00:03:19.460 --> 00:03:20.619
Where are we going?

00:03:20.620 --> 00:03:22.740
Almost there. We're nearly there.

00:03:25.200 --> 00:03:26.880
(Imperial Kitchen)

00:03:28.060 --> 00:03:31.699
Aren't we going
to find the Imperial Preceptor?

00:03:31.700 --> 00:03:34.139
We still have to eat first.

00:03:34.140 --> 00:03:37.139
Father, aren't you hungry
after carrying me for so long?

00:03:37.140 --> 00:03:38.539
I'm hungry.

00:03:38.540 --> 00:03:40.299
Only after we eat and have strength

00:03:40.300 --> 00:03:42.060
can we go drive away the bad people.

00:03:43.700 --> 00:03:44.820
Alright.

00:03:51.420 --> 00:03:53.260
Hurry, go.

00:03:53.580 --> 00:03:54.339
Hurry.

00:03:54.340 --> 00:03:56.340
If we delay, we'll all be punished.

00:03:58.700 --> 00:04:01.219
Those two have a foul smell on them.

00:04:01.220 --> 00:04:03.299
It's the same smell Wu Wang has.

00:04:03.300 --> 00:04:06.019
Those two must
be delivering food to Wu Wang.

00:04:06.020 --> 00:04:07.299
Let's follow them quickly.

00:04:07.300 --> 00:04:08.140
Mm.

00:04:37.160 --> 00:04:40.479
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:44.319
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:47.839
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:50.800
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:04:51.680 --> 00:04:55.319
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:04:55.320 --> 00:04:59.080
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:04:59.160 --> 00:05:02.479
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:02.480 --> 00:05:06.520
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:15.799
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:15.800 --> 00:05:19.439
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:23.159
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:23.160 --> 00:05:26.799
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:30.479
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:32.399
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:05:32.400 --> 00:05:38.600
♪Good fortune♪